message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and machine learning. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and audio tagging can be considered a form of language processing. cs.LG is another possible category as it deals with machine learning and classification tasks. cs.CV is also possible as it deals with computer vision and audio tagging can be considered a form of visual recognition. cs.NE is less likely as it deals with neural networks and this paper only uses CNNs.
